Package fr.xephi.authme.events

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AuthMeTeleportEvent
    This event is call when AuthMe try to teleport a player
    CustomEvent  
    FirstSpawnTeleportEvent
    Called if a player is teleported to the authme first spawn
    LoginEvent
    This event is called when a player login or register through AuthMe.
    LogoutEvent
    This event is called when a player logout through AuthMe.
    PasswordEncryptionEvent
    This event is called when we need to compare or get an hash password, for set a custom EncryptionMethod
    ProtectInventoryEvent
    This event is call just after store inventory into cache and will empty the player inventory.
    RegisterTeleportEvent
    This event is call if, and only if, a player is teleported just after a register.
    ResetInventoryEvent
    This event is call when a creative inventory is reseted.
    RestoreInventoryEvent
    This event restore the inventory from cache
    SpawnTeleportEvent
    Called if a player is teleported to a specific spawn
    StoreInventoryEvent
    This event is call just before write inventory content to cache
